                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Thomas: I understand you didn't accept the proposed solution, but this is still an important use case. If the proposed solution does not work, then work with the reporter to find a solution that supports phar as well as network and URI paths.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
